{
  "stem": "18572.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My most vivid memory is standing by a door that had a curtain in it-- it was a glass door-- and pushing aside that curtain.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I guess I knew that I wasn't supposed to be looking out because someone must have told me to.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was this public hanging.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were several people being hung there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had placards across their chest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And afterwards, I realized-- or at some point, someone explained to me that these were-- Jews had been caught smuggling food into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I remember them hanging there with this big sign across the chest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I just stood there, watching this thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just remember standing there, being horrified, and feeling guilty because I knew I wasn't supposed to be there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had arranged to have, I think, many members of our family to go into hiding with non-Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he paid them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the story I remember was that this particular man that-- he was a Volksdeutsch.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was supposed to keep us for the duration of the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he came to the house one day and told my father that we had to go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She didn't want to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I guess she just didn't want to believe that we had to leave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he kept insisting that we go that day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And for whatever reason, my father wasn't ready to leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe he was waiting for other members-- to arrange for the other members to leave.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But my mother, and I, and he were walking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were either in a field, or a cemetery, or something like a big, open space.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my mother was very upset with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
